Class Complex

  • java.lang.Object
    • math.Complex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Complex>, FieldElement<Complex>

    public final class Complex
extends Object
implements FieldElement<Complex>
    A representation of a complex number. This class is immutable and thread-safe.
